          "id": "nvidia-vera-rubin-production-2026-06",
          "title": "英伟达 Vera Rubin 平台进入量产并导入 CPO 网络",
          "summary": "英伟达在 GTC Taipei 宣布 Vera Rubin AI 工厂平台进入全面量产，台湾服务器厂商与全球供应链伙伴正在按规模制造相关系统，量产出货预计从今年秋季开始。该平台把 Vera CPU、Rubin GPU、BlueField-4、Spectrum-X Ethernet Photonics 等组合为面向 Agentic AI 的机架级系统，主要对应算力基础设施层，事件阶段已从发布走向供应链爬坡。",
          "sourceUrl": "https://investor.nvidia.com/news/press-release-details/2026/NVIDIA-Vera-Rubin-Ramps-Into-Full-Production-to-Power-Agentic-AI-Factories-Worldwide/default.aspx",
